headline: Linde Named One of Ethisphere’s 2025 World's Most Ethical Companies®
summary: WOKING, England, April 23, 2025--Linde (Nasdaq: LIN) today announced it has been included in the 2025 World's Most Ethical Companies® list for the fifth consecutive year.
